title: Into Her Chambers
description: Somewhere off the Orange County coastline sits a legendary shipwreck. On a stormy night, the ship went down with the Captain's wife's jewels--something every California treasure hunter swoons over.Drawn by the lure of jewels and driven by unconsolable grief, Luke solo dives deep into the ship's chambers, unprepared for what he might find lurking in the deep.
author: Jennifer Arnett
